parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.

Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to jerk, hesitate, or fail to move, leading to accidents, loss of control, or stranding. It can also lead to costly repairs and potentially cause a fire due to oil leaks.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or hesitates while driving
fails to move forward or backward

symptoms: The vehicle stalls intermittently while driving

and other electrical systems may malfunction.
